{"tid":1839581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"11月8日大家悼念緊周梓樂同學既時候 呢班人竟然咁做 重上埋神枱","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T14:43:18.000Z","uid":128118,"like":38,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"572392c699b51cd9207de9c4be76ff2ecc21f7b0","tid":1839581,"uid":128118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:16:08.000Z","msg":"周同學被宣布死個日 大家係出面悼念同打生打死既時候 另一邊廂 一班自稱同路人既人竟然係到嘻嘻哈哈慶祝生日 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QeUMca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QeUMca.png&h=524c12ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你以為咁樣已經夠仆街？ 未算 呢班人借住黃店既名彈起 由冇人識到而加個個都狗衝去佢個年宵 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtAQjxn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtAQjxn.png&h=7f274661&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qAVEcSp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqAVEcSp.png&h=965ebfca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就算大家話我係熱狗或者分化撚都好 但係周同學既死對我黎講係好大件事 連悼念都冇去既人 絕對唔係同路人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/16n7mMV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F16n7mMV.jpg&h=9c4453b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果我地唔認清邊個先係真正既同路人 我地死去既朋友係唔會原諒我地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">黃色Partyroom 唔係淨係得一間 希望大家認清邊d係同路人 邊d係食人血饅頭既仆街</span>"},{"pid":"37801da8e56f71cd88e9dc057cb5a582fa977b25","tid":1839581,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"去黃大仙，槍頭香，大仙佑香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839313</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1594400b3b4a1013480d35a750f1bc51c07504f7","tid":1839581,"uid":128118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"Push(1/10)"},{"pid":"3bbe871ed7f70e20c05ee7660cf7fad0ba90bf46","tid":1839581,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep